cast.overview: Retreating from life after a tragedy, a man questions the universe by writing to Love, Time and Death. Receiving unexpected answers, he begins to see how these things interlock and how even loss can reveal moments of meaning and beauty.
cast.title: Collateral Beauty

details.biography: Elia Monte-Brown was born and raised in the East Village, New York City, as the daughter of choreographers Elisa Monte and David Brown. She is an actress, teacher, writer, and strident feminist, and graduated from The Yale School of Drama.
details.name: Elia Monte-Brown
details.place_of_birth: East Village, New York City, New York, USA
